					<lb n="14r=14"/>ṉāpatiyā((tiyā))kiya civakumāraṉ centil āpatipatiyāki  
					<lb n="15r=15"/>ya Āṟumuka nayiṉār cuppiṟamaṇiya cuvāmi paripūṟaṉa kiṭā  
					<lb n="16r=16"/>ṣa vīṣṭṭaṇamāka Eḷuntaruḷi yirukkum caṉṉitā  
					<lb n="17r=17"/>ṉa-t tirukkōpura-t tiruppaṇit taṟmam civa-puṇṇiya  
					<lb n="18r=18"/>ttukku  naṭuvu maṇṭalam vaṇita cēkaram cōḷa va  
					<lb n="19r=19"/>ḷaṉāṭāṉ niṭacēpa nati tīram cāttūr neṉmēṉi  
					<lb n="20r=20"/>vaṭamalaipuram vaṇita cēkaram Acēṣa viṟṟuva makācaṉa  
					<lb n="21r=21"/>ṅkaḷum tāṉāṉattār talattār Āṟāṟu kāḷa piḷḷai  
					<lb n="22r=22"/>mār ‌mutalimār ṉāyakkamār kavaṟaic ceṭṭiyaḷ  
					<lb n="23r=23"/>reṭṭiyaḷ toṭṭiyar koṉaṅkaḷ tēvamār  
					<lb n="24r=24"/>kavaṇṭamār cēṭar kaikkaḷar kaṇmāḷar Añ  
					<lb n="25r=25"/>cu cātiyārum vāṇiyar kāvalakkāṟar viṟṟu vā  
					<lb n="26r=26"/>ṅkicar tāciyaḷ paṇikkamār cavaḷakāṟar kucavar ṉā  
					<lb n="27r=27"/>ṭākkaḷ vaṇṇār ṉāvitar cemmāṉ paḷḷaṉ paṟai  
					<lb n="28r=28"/>yaṉ cakkiliyaṉ yitu mutalākiya ṉāṅku cātiyiluḷ  
					<lb n="29r=29"/>ḷavarkaḷōm cakala caṉa cammatiyāka Āṟumuka nayiṉa  
					<lb n="30r=30"/>r caṉṉitāṉat tirukōpura-t-tiruppaṇi-t taṟma  
					<lb n="31r=31"/>m civapuṇṇiyattukku-t tāṉacātaṉa-p-paṭṭaiyam ā  
					<lb n="32r=31"/>vatu Eṅkaḷ cēkara vaṇitam mūṉṟukkum {varuṣam} 1 k=ku kaṭ  
					<lb n="33r=33"/>ṭiṉa vīṭṭukku {varuṣam} 1 k=ku āṟuṅkālppaṭikkuk kuṟu  
					<lb n="34r=34"/>ṇi-t tavaca vītam vīṭṭu-t tukaivari ōlaippaṭikku  
					<lb n="35r=35"/>p-piṟavattakañ ceyyiṟa makācaṉaṅkaḷ nāṭṭ(ā/ara)  
					<lb n="36r=36"/>ṇmaikkāṟar kaṇakka-p piḷḷaimār taṇṭalkkā  
					<lb n="37r=37"/>ṟar muṉṉiṉṟu tavacam niluvai viṭāmal-c cēkarañ  
					<lb n="38r=38"/>ceytu caṉṉitāṉa muttirai maṉuṭar vantarvarkaḷu  
					<lb n="39r=39"/>kkēṟka Aḷantu kuṭuttu varuvōm ākavum Inta paṭi  
					<lb n="40r=40"/>kku-c cakala-caṉa-cammatiyāka-t taṟma-cātaṉap paṭṭai  
					<lb n="41r=41"/>yam eḷuti-k kuṭutta paṭiyiṉālē Aṭṣaram tappāmal  
					<lb n="42r=42"/>naṭantu koḷvōm ākavum Inta taṟmam Ikapara  
					<lb n="43r=43"/>m raṇṭukkum tikaṭṭāta kaṉiyāka-c cuvāmi vali  
					<lb n="44r=44"/>yt ‌taṭuttāḷ-k koṇṭaruḷiṉa paṭiyiṉālē  
					<lb n="45r=45"/>yintat taṟmattukku yātām orutar paripāl(I>a)  
					<lb n="46r=46"/>ṉam paṇṇiṉavarkaḷ tavacam niluvai viṭāma  
					<lb n="47r=47"/>l-c cēkarañ ceytu vicēṣṭamāka vanta vi  
					<lb n="48r=48"/>ravuñ ceytu kuṭuttavarkaḷ puttira pavuttira pāra  
					
				</p>
				
				
